description: Try our easy to follow Autumn Vegetable Flan recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Autumn Vegetable Flan Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Meanwhile, whisk eggs and cream in a jug. Stir in cheese. Spread pumpkin and leeks over pastry. Top with carrots and gently pour egg mixture between carrots. Bake for 35 minutes or until set. Top with chives, to serve.
